## 20. General

20.1 **Order of precedence.** In the event of any conflict between (a) this Agreement, (b) the GTCs, (c) the SLA, (d) the Compliance Annex, or (e) any Order, the order of precedence shall be **(a), (b), (d), (c), (e)**. For the avoidance of doubt, **this Agreement (as may be amended by the Parties) shall prevail over the GTCs**.
